OL,3,C'Calm before the storm': Inflation
OL,4,Cfalls to 2.6% ahead of April's rising
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FEconomists have warned of a sharp rise
OL,8,Fin inflation to 3.6% this month -
OL,9,Fdriven by an increase in household
OL,10,Fbills. ITV News Business and Economics
OL,11,FEditor Joel Hills reports
OL,13,FUK inflation has fallen to 2.6%, but
OL,14,Feconomists have warned this is the
OL,15,F"calm before the storm" of April's
OL,16,Frising bills.
OL,18,FIt represents a second consecutive dip
OL,19,Fafter inflation eased by more than
OL,20,Fexpected to 2.8% in February on the
OL,21,Fback of lower clothing prices.
