OL,3,C'Calm before the storm': Inflation
OL,4,Cfalls to 2.6% ahead of April's rising
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FSpeaking on Wednesday, Chancellor
OL,8,FRachel Reeves said: "Inflation falling
OL,9,Ffor two months in a row, wages growing
OL,10,Ffaster than prices, and positive
OL,11,Fgrowth figures are encouraging signs
OL,12,Fthat our plan for change is working,
OL,13,Fbut there is more to be done.
OL,15,F"I know many families are still
OL,16,Fstruggling with the cost of living and
OL,17,Fthis is an anxious time because of a
OL,18,Fchanging world.
