OL,3,C'Calm before the storm': Inflation
OL,4,Cfalls to 2.6% ahead of April's rising
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,F"A base effect from alcohol and
OL,8,Ftobacco prices a year ago should
OL,9,Fsubtract another three basis points
OL,10,F(0.03 percentage points) from headline
OL,11,FCPI inflation."
OL,13,FHe added that the potential reduction
OL,14,Fin price rises would be "the calm
OL,15,Fbefore the storm of April price hikes,
OL,16,Fwhich should drive up headline
OL,17,Finflation to 3.6%".
