OL,7,FThe Bank of England has also said
OL,8,Finflation is likely to increase
OL,9,Fthrough this year and peak at around
OL,10,F3.7% later this summer.
OL,12,FThe figure will be the last inflation
OL,13,Freading that the Bank's monetary
OL,14,Fpolicy committee will receive before
OL,15,Fthey vote on whether to reduce
OL,16,Finterest rates ` which currently sits
OL,17,Fat 4.5% ` at their meeting next month.
